---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Carson Underwood"
  description="Privacy policy for apps developed by Carson Underwood."
>
  <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800 p-8 shadow-xl">
    <h1 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-100">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-8 font-mono text-xs text-slate-500">Last updated: March 12, 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-300">
      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-slate-100">Overview</h2>
        <p>
          This privacy policy applies to all applications developed and published by Carson
          Underwood ("I", "me", or "my"). I am committed to protecting your privacy. This policy
          describes what information is (and is not) collected when you use my apps.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-slate-100">Information I Do Not Collect</h2>
        <p>
          My applications do not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal information. This
          includes, but is not limited to:
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li class="flex gap-2 text-slate-400"><span class="text-cyan-500 select-none">›</span><span>Name, email address, or other contact information</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-2 text-slate-400"><span class="text-cyan-500 select-none">›</span><span>Location or device identifiers</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-2 text-slate-400"><span class="text-cyan-500 select-none">›</span><span>Usage data, analytics, or crash reports sent to external servers</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-2 text-slate-400"><span class="text-cyan-500 select-none">›</span><span>Any data you enter or generate while using the app</span></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-slate-100">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          My applications do not integrate with third-party analytics, advertising, or data
          collection services. No data about you or your usage is sent to any third party.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-slate-100">Data Storage</h2>
        <p>
          Any data you create or input within an app is stored locally on your device only. I have
          no access to this data.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-slate-100">Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          My applications do not knowingly collect any information from anyone, including children
          under the age of 13.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-slate-100">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          If this policy changes in the future, the updated version will be posted at this URL with
          a revised "last updated" date.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-slate-100">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this privacy policy, you can reach me at{' '}
          <a href="/contact" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">cunderw.dev/contact</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
